fulltitle: JOE HENDERSON on CACE INT'L TV
description:
This is an EPK from Verve and Polygram Records sent to CACE INT'L TV  for promotional purposes. Here Joe talks about doing this tribute to Miles Davis.

A copy of this show is available for purchase. For information contact:   fikishac@gmail.com

As Cultural Historians, CACE INT'L TV showcases the  art , music and culture of our international creative artists, continuing to bring the best to our international audience.

CACE INT'L TV, a 30 minute show,  airs  online weekly on Wednesday on the Internet world wide:
LINK:    www.BRICartsmedia.org 
Click TV SHOWS & VIDEOS  
 Scroll down to  BROOKLYN FREE SPEECH LIVE

In Brooklyn the show airs on cable television on Time Warner (#34) ;Cablevision (#67) ; RCN (#82) ; and in all of NYC on Verizon Fios (#42 ) 
           WEDNESDAY @ 1:30 pm & 9:30 pm  (New York time). (EST)

This network has been nominated for a 2016 Network Emmy Award.
CACE INT'L TV has over a half million views (You Tube/ caceinterntional.com/ google +)
